-    else ifneq ($$(filter %.s %.S, $$($1_FILENAME)), )
-      # Compile as assembler file
+      $1_DEP_FLAG := $(GENDEPS_FLAGS)
+    else ifneq ($$(filter %.S, $$($1_FILENAME)), )

+      $1_FLAGS := $$($1_BASE_ASFLAGS)
+      $1_COMPILER := $(AS)
+      $1_DEP_FLAG := $(GENDEPS_FLAGS)
+    else ifneq ($$(filter %.s, $$($1_FILENAME)), )
+      # Compile as non-preprocessed assembler file
